latestIgtvVideos.title: #StayStrongIndia
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
With the power of community & togetherness, heading towards a better tomorrow.

In support of their colleagues and their families back here in India, #Coach team members from across the globe have put together these heartfelt messages & pictures to spread the word #StayStrongIndia. And we are really touched by this gesture!

Along with this, the Coach Foundation and the Kate Spade New York Foundation have donated $1,00,000 to Direct Relief, to help mobilize much-needed critical oxygen concentration devices to medical facilities across the country. To date, Tapestry & its foundations have donated over $10M in financial contribution and product donations to support COVID-19 relief globally. 

We truly are proud of such partnerships!

@tapestry @coach @katespadeny @directrelief 
@tewari.vaibhav  @aru_the_fighter @lisaeberhardt_ @deepikagehani 

#Tapestry #CovidRelief #CovidSupport #StaySafeiIdia #Coach #KateSpade #LifeAtCoach #InThisTogether2021 #WeShallOvercome

latestPosts.caption:
Team RBL had the incredible opportunity to witness the Zegna SS’26 Fashion Show and explore Villa Zegna at the iconic Dubai Opera House — marking the brand’s first-ever show outside of Italy! ✨
 
Alessandro Sartori’s visionary showcase blurred borders, seamlessly merging the Founder’s residence in Trivero with the vastness of the desert, set against a live musical score curated and performed by James Blake. The following day saw Dubai Opera reimagined as Villa Zegna — a space that paid homage to Zegna’s rich heritage and modern elegance. 
 
The three day curated itinerary was complete with immersive moments including a heritage retrospective at the Arts Museum, panoramic views from the top of the Burj Khalifa, and a glimpse into tomorrow at the Museum of the Future — all complemented by a rich tapestry of global cuisines and local delicacies!🤩

#RelianceBrandsLimited #RBL #ZEGNASummer26 #VillaZegna

Capri, the Armani way✨

Sawai Padmanabh Singh made a striking appearance at Giorgio Armani Mare’s latest stop in Capri, dressed in Giorgio Armani. Hosted in the iconic island setting, the event brought to life the brand’s high summer spirit. 

A blend of Riviera glamour and refined design, the event marked yet another chapter in Armani’s global holiday tour, filled with yachts, boutique takeovers, and beachside chic! ☀️

#RelianceBrandsLimited #RBL #GiorgioArmani #RBLDressing

A magical new chapter begins as Hamleys opened its doors at The Avenues, Kuwait on May 31st! ✨

With a vibrant 1170 sqm space full of imagination, the store brings together classic characters, live theatre, interactive play zones, and over 10,000 toys under one roof. Whether it’s racing at Ralleyz, crafting accessories at The Boutique, or just meeting the Hamley Bear — it’s a place where joy lives around every corner. 

This marks Hamleys’ 9th GCC store, and one of the most enchanting ones yet! 🎈
